name: Baijnath Foods Private Limited
overview: Established in the year 2010, at Delhi (India), we, “Baijnath Foods Private Limited”, are recognized as the ISO 22001: 2005, FSMS certified organization instrumental in manufacturing, exporting, trading and supplying a comprehensive assortment of superior quality Spices and Papad, under the brand name of Swadam Spices. We are Specialized in Providing Meat Masala, Chana Masala, Garam Masala, Chicken Masala & Curry powder. The offered product range comprises Jeera, Saunf, Ajwain, Kali Mirch, Garam Masala, Kali Sarson, Peeli Sarson, Rai, Dalchini, Haldi Powder, Mirch Powder, Cardamom, etc. These agro products are processed using the best grade raw ingredients and sophisticated technology under the most hygienic conditions. Apart from this, these are packed with high precision in order to meet the international quality standards
